  "type": "feat",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 1st level, you grow claws. These claws are treated as natural weapons, allowing you to make two claw attacks as a full attack, using your full base attack bonus. These attacks deal 1d6 points of damage each (1d4 if you are Small) plus your Strength modifier.</p>\n<p>At 4th level, these claws are considered magic weapons for the purpose of overcoming damage reduction.</p>\n<p>At 8th level, the damage increases to 1d8 points (1d6 if you are Small).</p>\n<p>At 12th level, these claws deal an additional 1d6 points of damage of your energy type on a hit.</p>",
